welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Summit View! This charming city is known for its breathtaking views and friendly locals. We invite you to explore and experience all that Summit View has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Industrial Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Industrial Airport handles all freight and cargo operations.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal A
terminals.description: This terminal serves domestic and international flights operated by Alaska Airlines, American Airlines, Delta Air Lines, and JetBlue.

terminals.name: Terminal B
terminals.description: This terminal serves domestic and international flights operated by Air Canada, Frontier Airlines, Hawaiian Airlines, and Sun Country Airlines.

terminals.name: Terminal C
terminals.description: This terminal serves domestic and international flights operated by United Airlines and its partner airlines.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves domestic and international flights operated by Alaska Airlines and its partner airlines.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves domestic and international flights operated by Delta Air Lines and its partner airlines.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport.
